@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant App
participant API
database DB

User -> App: Opens Home Screen
App -> App: Request Vehicle Status
App -> API: Request Vehicle Data (SoC, Consumption, Temperature)
API -> DB: Retrieve Vehicle Data
activate DB
DB --> API: Vehicle Data (SoC, Consumption, Temperature)
deactivate DB
activate API
API -> API: Calculate Estimated Range
API --> App: Vehicle Status (Range, SoC, Temperature)
deactivate API
App -> App: Display Vehicle Status
App --> User: Display Vehicle Status on Home Screen

alt No Data Available
    App -> API: Request Vehicle Data (SoC, Consumption, Temperature)
    API -> DB: Retrieve Vehicle Data
    activate DB
    DB --> API: Error: No Data Available
    deactivate DB
    API --> App: Error: No Data Available
    deactivate API
    App --> User: Display "Vehicle Data Unavailable" Error Message
else Calculation Error
    App -> API: Request Vehicle Data (SoC, Consumption, Temperature)
    API -> DB: Retrieve Vehicle Data
    activate DB
    DB --> API: Vehicle Data (SoC, Consumption, Temperature)
    deactivate DB
    API -> API: Calculate Estimated Range
    API -> API: Exception Occurred During Calculation
    API --> App: Error: Calculation Error
    deactivate API
    App --> User: Display "Range Calculation Error" Message
end

@enduml